{"title_page": "Veronica Bekoe", "text_new": "{{short description|Ghanaian Biological Scientist}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Veronica Bekoe\n| image              = \n| imagesize          = \n| alt                = \n| caption            = \n| birth_date         = \n| birth_place        = \n| othername          = \n| citizenship        = Ghanaian\n| education          = Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology\n| occupation         = Biological Scientist\n| yearsactive        = \n| website            = \n| notable_work       = [[Veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]]\n}}\n'''Veronica Bekoe '''is a [[Biological]] Scientist from [[Ghana]]. She is known for her impact in the [[invention]] and  [[Discovery (observation)|discovery]] of the [[veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]] used to reduce the spread of communicable diseases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfhss.org/our-team/mrs-veronica-bekoe/|title=Mrs. Veronica Bekoe|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ghanatogether.org/HTML/Projects/Sanitation.html|title=Ghana Together Health and Sanitation Projects|website=ghanatogether.org|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref>\n\n== Education ==\nVeronica attended [[Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology|Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology (KNUST)]] where she obtained Bachelors of Science in Biology in Biological Science between 1968 \u2013 1972.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://yen.com.gh/151351-meet-veronica-bekoe-woman-ingenious-veronica-buckets.html|title=Meet Veronica Bekoe the genius Ghanaian woman who invented veronica buckets|last=Quist|first=Ebenezer|date=2020-03-25|website=Yen.com.gh - Ghana news.|language=en|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nHer career in the [[Ghana Health Service|Ghana Health Service (GHS)]] spanned from 1972-2008, working at the Public Health and Reference Laboratory, worked as a prime person for the National AIDS/STI  Control Program and also has over 30 years experience in medical laboratory practice.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://kuulpeeps.com/2020/03/veronica-bekoe-the-ghanaian-inventor-of-the-life-saving-veronica-buckets/|title=Veronica Bekoe: The Ghanaian Inventor Of The Life Saving Veronica Buckets {{!}} Kuulpeeps - Ghana Campus News and Lifestyle Site by Students|last=Tetteh|first=Nii Okai|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfhss.org/our-team/mrs-veronica-bekoe/|title=Mrs. Veronica Bekoe \u2013 CfHSS|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref>\n\n== Achievement ==\nVeronica is noted for her invention of the [[Veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]]. The bucket was invented to curb or reduce [[Cholera]], [[Diarrhea|Diarrhoea]] among other diseases. In 2020, the bucket was widely used in the [[Africa|African]] continent  and the global community to fight the novel pandemic [[Coronavirus]] (COVID-19) or SARS-COV-2.<ref name=\":0\" /> Her discovery and invention of the veronica bucket was as result of a problem or gap she identified in her field of work, she noticed that there was a challenge with running water and they had to use a bowl of water to wash their hands after medical work in-turns which was very dangerous to their health because everyone had to use the same water until it becomes dirty,seeing the health implications she created a [[prototype]] bucket with a tap attached to an aluminium utensils used in selling [[Hausa koko]], popularly known as '''Akorlaa gyae su''' which has now become the veronica bucket recognized globally.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/I-invented-the-Veronica-Buckets-for-my-colleague-biological-scientists-Veronica-Bekoe-908659|title=I invented the Veronica Buckets for my colleague biological scientists - Veronica Bekoe|website=www.ghanaweb.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/general-news/veronica-bucket-inventor-seeks-government-support-for-patenting.html|title=Veronica Bucket inventor seeks government support for patenting|website=Graphic Online|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lr9uRxbrdp8|title=Veronica Bucket-Interview of the Ghanaian prof who created it|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ucF92u8eMzQ|title=Time with Veronica Bekoe (Designer of the Veronica Bucket)|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VMNCXOYdtg0|title=HOW ''VERONICA BUCKET'' WAS INVENTED BY MADAM VERONICA BEKOE|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wP4JvkjOdEk|title=SHE INVENTED THE VERONICA BUCKET BUT HMM: SHE TELLS HER STORY|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bekoe, Veronica}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women biologists]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian biologists]]\n\n{{Ghana-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Ghanaian Biological Scientist}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Veronica Bekoe\n| image              = \n| imagesize          = \n| alt                = \n| caption            = \n| birth_date         = \n| birth_place        = \n| othername          = \n| citizenship        = Ghanaian\n| education          = Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology\n| occupation         = Biological Scientist\n| yearsactive        = \n| website            = \n| notable_work       = [[Veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]]\n}}\n'''Veronica Bekoe '''is a [[Biological]] Scientist from [[Ghana]]. She is known for her impact in the [[invention]] and  [[Discovery (observation)|discovery]] of the [[veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]] used to reduce the spread of communicable diseases.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfhss.org/our-team/mrs-veronica-bekoe/|title=Mrs. Veronica Bekoe|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ghanatogether.org/HTML/Projects/Sanitation.html|title=Ghana Together Health and Sanitation Projects|website=ghanatogether.org|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref>\n\n== Education ==\nVeronica attended [[Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology|Kwame Nkrumah University of Science and Technology (KNUST)]] where she obtained Bachelors of Science in Biology in Biological Science between 1968 \u2013 1972.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://yen.com.gh/151351-meet-veronica-bekoe-woman-ingenious-veronica-buckets.html|title=Meet Veronica Bekoe the genius Ghanaian woman who invented veronica buckets|last=Quist|first=Ebenezer|date=2020-03-25|website=Yen.com.gh - Ghana news.|language=en|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nHer career in the [[Ghana Health Service|Ghana Health Service (GHS)]] spanned from 1972-2008, working at the Public Health and Reference Laboratory, worked as a prime person for the National AIDS/STI  Control Program and also has over 30 years experience in medical laboratory practice.<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://kuulpeeps.com/2020/03/veronica-bekoe-the-ghanaian-inventor-of-the-life-saving-veronica-buckets/|title=Veronica Bekoe: The Ghanaian Inventor Of The Life Saving Veronica Buckets {{!}} Kuulpeeps - Ghana Campus News and Lifestyle Site by Students|last=Tetteh|first=Nii Okai|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfhss.org/our-team/mrs-veronica-bekoe/|title=Mrs. Veronica Bekoe \u2013 CfHSS|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref>\n\n== Achievement ==\nVeronica is noted for her invention of the [[Veronica bucket|Veronica Bucket]]. The bucket was invented to curb or reduce [[Cholera]], [[Diarrhea|Diarrhoea]] among other diseases. In 2020, the bucket was widely used in the [[African]] continent  and the global community to fight the novel pandemic [[Coronavirus]] (COVID-19) or SARS-COV-2.<ref name=\":0\" /> Her discovery and invention of the veronica bucket was as result of a problem or gap she identified in her field of work, she noticed that there was a challenge with running water and they had to use a bowl of water to wash their hands after medical work in-turns which was very dangerous to their health because everyone had to use the same water until it becomes dirty,seeing the health implications she created a [[prototype]] bucket with a tap attached to an aluminium utensils used in selling [[Hausa koko]], popularly known as '''Akorlaa gyae su''' which has now become the veronica bucket recognized globally.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/I-invented-the-Veronica-Buckets-for-my-colleague-biological-scientists-Veronica-Bekoe-908659|title=I invented the Veronica Buckets for my colleague biological scientists - Veronica Bekoe|website=www.ghanaweb.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/general-news/veronica-bucket-inventor-seeks-government-support-for-patenting.html|title=Veronica Bucket inventor seeks government support for patenting|website=Graphic Online|language=en-gb|access-date=2020-04-27}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lr9uRxbrdp8|title=Veronica Bucket-Interview of the Ghanaian prof who created it|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ucF92u8eMzQ|title=Time with Veronica Bekoe (Designer of the Veronica Bucket)|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VMNCXOYdtg0|title=HOW ''VERONICA BUCKET'' WAS INVENTED BY MADAM VERONICA BEKOE|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wP4JvkjOdEk|title=SHE INVENTED THE VERONICA BUCKET BUT HMM: SHE TELLS HER STORY|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bekoe, Veronica}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women biologists]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian biologists]]\n\n{{Ghana-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Rodw", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toAfrican(link changed toAfrica) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Veronica_Bekoe"}
